    "Nevertheless, nearly onefifth reported feeling absolutely confident in their use of the chat, while only 10.7% reported feeling not confident at all [Mean 3.9 (SD = 1.1) on a scale of 1-5].",
    "Perceptions of ChatGPTTable 2 presents the mean scores regarding both the positive and negative perceptions of ChatGPT among the study population.",
    "The data reveal a generally positive attitude towards ChatGPT use, with an overall mean score of 4.04 (SD = 0.62) on a scale from 1 to 5, where a higher score indicates a more favorable perception of the positive impacts.",
